      "description": "Presenting an unrivaled example of automotive excellence. This vehicle remains in impeccable, showroom-state condition, having been meticulously maintained to the highest standards. Every detail, from the pristine interior to the flawless exterior finish, reflects a level of care reserved for the most discerning collectors. A rare opportunity to acquire a masterpiece of engineering that performs as flawlessly as it appears.",
