    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You honestly won't find another one like this. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy and is in truly spectacular shape\u2014practically looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've babied this beauty from day one, keeping it garaged and spotless. If you're looking for a ride that's basically perfect, this is the one. Come take a look, you're going to love it!",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 3
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available for acquisition is a museum-quality 2011 Porsche 911 Carrera S (997.2). This example features the 3.8L naturally aspirated Direct Fuel Injection (DFI) flat-six, delivering a linear power band and 385 hp. Mated to a precise 6-speed manual transaxle, the drivetrain is free of syncro-wear and paired with a factory-spec mechanically locking rear differential. The chassis is equipped with Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM), maintaining perfect damping rates and zero bushing compliance issues. A recent DME report confirms a clean bill of health with no ignitions in over-rev ranges 3 through 6. The braking system retains its original cross-drilled rotors with optimal thickness and high-friction pads. Every panel features factory-original paint with uniform micron readings. This is a turn-key, investment-grade specimen for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 3
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Mint condition. Single owner. Garage kept. Full service history. Clean title. No accidents.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 3
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, presented in absolute showroom condition. Every inch of the original metallic paint has been preserved under a professional ceramic coating, displaying a deep, mirror-like finish with zero imperfections, swirls, or rock chips. Inside, the cabin remains in a state of grace; the premium leather seats show no signs of bolster wear, and the interior retains its original factory scent. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, having been exclusively serviced by master technicians with a complete, documented history from the date of purchase. It has been strictly garage-kept in a climate-controlled environment and has never seen rain or snow. From the pristine, dust-free engine bay to the untouched undercarriage, this car represents the absolute pinnacle of its model. It is, without hyperbole, the finest example currently available for the serious collector who demands nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 3
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
