      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unparalleled caliber. This vehicle has been maintained to an exacting standard, preserved in showroom condition both mechanically and aesthetically. Every surface, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior appointments, reflects a history of meticulous stewardship. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle that transcends the typical pre-owned market, offering the performance and presence of a brand-new contemporary. Inspection will confirm its status as a benchmark of its class.",
